page.title: 11SCHOOL GIRL'S DAY SKEGNESS
page.content: At 8 'o clock I get up and make my mum and dad a cup of tea.Then I get dressed and have my breakfast.Usually my breakst is a bowl of cereal like bran flakes with milk on them.I don't bother with a drink in the morning. After breakfast I brush my teeth and hair put on my shoes and set off for school. At schoolI do some spellings and some maths and then at 1030 it is play time.After play I come in and do some reading and other English.By that time it is lunch and I go home.I have snack soup,a Trio chocolate biscuit and some sandwiches.At 1300 I go back to school until 1530 when I go home then I go out to play some times.I like to play tennis in the street with my friends or my mum.
